img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:06:56.000Z","msg":"香港殿堂級Diva 再次穿上露肩服裝,<br />\n打扮成Tinker Bell 奇妙仙子, 為大家同中樂團獻唱<br />\n李清照所寫嘅 《聲慢慢》<br />\n一齊欣賞汪阿姐嘅歌喉啦~~~<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O8MtVX-AggE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO8MtVX-AggE&d=ipgdt2tu1YhOaEKRl7sZsACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f5fa72ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O8MtVX-AggE</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️注意:&quot;靚聲位&quot; (引號)<br />\n<br />\n最美麗亞洲真人版Tinker Bell 示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/212808_fdf8ab615823a6f09291d899ed0a9e14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F212808_fdf8ab615823a6f09291d899ed0a9e14.png&h=c9aa3b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4:20 到黃<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">昏&uarr;&uarr;點&uarr;&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><em>屌&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</em></strong></span></span>滴滴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J8WKeUr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJ8WKeUr.gif&h=61d50d20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋尋覓覓，冷冷清清，淒淒慘慘戚戚。乍暖還寒時候，最難將息。三盃兩盞淡酒，3:24怎敵他晚來<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">風&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>急！<br />\n3:31 雁過也，正傷心，卻是舊時<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;相~~~ng~~&rdquo;</span></span>識。(chok 咪)　<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/u3Vbv7x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fu3Vbv7x.gif&h=32e630fd&s={SIZE}\" />　<br />\n<br />\n3:42 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;滿&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;~~~~~~&rdquo;</span></span>地黃<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">花&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;~~~</span></span>堆積。<br />\n<br />\n3:51<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;憔&rdquo;</span></span>悴<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">損↗↘</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如&darr;&darr;&darr;↕↕↕↕</span></span>今有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誰&darr;&darr;&darr;↕↕↕↕堪&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;摘&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;？守&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;~~~&ldquo;wuwuwuwuu&rdquo;</span></span> 著<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">窗&uarr;&uarr;↗↘兒iiiii&ldquo;iar&rdquo;~~</span></span>，獨<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;自&rdquo;</span></span>怎<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生&uarr;&uarr;得&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;黑&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;~~~~~~</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n4:10(情深款款的樣子)<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;梧&rdquo;</span></span>桐<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更&uarr;&uarr;&ldquo;兼&uarr;&uarr;&rdquo;</span></span>細雨，到黃<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">昏&uarr;&uarr; 點&uarr;&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">屌&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>滴滴。這次第，怎一個愁字了<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">得~~~~~！ </span></span>"},{"pid":"87a7ff288644fd487a8e9c931e00acf130cc8ba0","tid":796370,"uid":24160,"like":53,"dislike":3,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:07:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阿姐服裝回顧</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"https://lumiere-a.akamaihd.net/v1/images/2b65901707e2087367946f7b7772fd8335c6c9e5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flumiere-a.akamaihd.net%2Fv1%2Fimages%2F2b65901707e2087367946f7b7772fd8335c6c9e5.jpeg&h=26fa0878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最美麗亞洲真人版Tinker Bell 示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/212808_fdf8ab615823a6f09291d899ed0a9e14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F212808_fdf8ab615823a6f09291d899ed0a9e14.png&h=c9aa3b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/213002_ed566d5a18e303ffbbc1dab08e178150.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F213002_ed566d5a18e303ffbbc1dab08e178150.png&h=3661effc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然奇妙仙子甩咗對fairy wings, 但仍能吸引局長與牠合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/213234_539d973130ba19270da4cffe256669f6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F213234_539d973130ba19270da4cffe256669f6.png&h=385128d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奇妙仙子笑容親切大方<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/213337_44b4657cdd50c69ddd3edd7b8bbeab1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F213337_44b4657cdd50c69ddd3edd7b8bbeab1e.png&h=d1893ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奇妙仙子件衫離咗罩添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\nTube top 個尖端位重可以幫婆婆騷癢<br />\n抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/0