g src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d364730c338312a850f81663f65882da152e08","tid":796370,"uid":73849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"等咗你好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1106de6fb6e690d796fdd9d571a8c3b0f92f6303","tid":796370,"uid":174289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:05:18.000Z","msg":"經過那些年"},{"pid":"56510e46632e6a6fdedeec97088bb933c9717de5","tid":796370,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b5a5a78090cd05bd64e9ebcbe57400345267910f","tid":796370,"uid":24160,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"quote":{"pid":"f86fc9129b6f22d0ba82a37166151ea283ddd101","tid":796370,"uid":22422,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:03:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>經過那些～年～～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:06:56.000Z","msg":"香港殿堂級Diva 再次穿上露肩服裝,<br />\n打扮成Tinker Bell 奇妙仙子, 為大家同中樂團獻唱<br />\n李清照所寫嘅 《聲慢慢》<br />\n一齊欣賞汪阿姐嘅歌喉啦~~~<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O8MtVX-AggE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO8MtVX-AggE&d=ipgdt2tu1YhOaEKRl7sZsACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f5fa72ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O8MtVX-AggE</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️注意:&quot;靚聲位&quot; (引號)<br />\n<br />\n最美麗亞洲真人版Tinker Bell 示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/212808_fdf8ab615823a6f09291d899ed0a9e14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F212808_fdf8ab615823a6f09291d899ed0a9e14.png&h=c9aa3b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4:20 到黃<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">昏&uarr;&uarr;點&uarr;&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><em>屌&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</em></strong></span></span>滴滴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J8WKeUr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJ8WKeUr.gif&h=61d50d20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋尋覓覓，冷冷清清，淒淒慘慘戚戚。乍暖還寒時候，最難將息。三盃兩盞淡酒，3:24怎敵他晚來<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">風&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>急！<br />\n3:31 雁過也，正傷心，卻是舊時<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;相~~~ng~~&rdquo;</span></span>識。(chok 咪)　<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/u3Vbv7x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fu3Vbv7x.gif&h=32e630fd&s={SIZE}\" />　<br />\n<br />\n3:42 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;滿&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;~~~~~~&rdquo;</span></span>地黃<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">花&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;~~~</span></span>堆積。<br />\n<br />\n3:51<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;憔&rdquo;</span></span>悴<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">損↗↘</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如&darr;&darr;&darr;↕↕↕↕</span></span>今有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誰&darr;&darr;&darr;↕↕↕↕堪&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;摘&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;？守&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;~~~&ldquo;wuwuwuwuu&rdquo;</span></span> 著<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">窗&uarr;&uarr;↗↘兒iiiii&ldquo;iar&rdquo;~~</span></span>，獨<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;自&rdquo;</span></span>怎<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生&uarr;&uarr;得&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;黑&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;~~~~~~</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n4:10(情深款款的樣子)<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;梧&rdquo;</span></span>桐<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更&uarr;&uarr;&ldquo;兼&uarr;&uarr;&rdquo;</span></span>細雨，到黃<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">昏&uarr;&uarr; 點&uarr;&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">屌&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>滴滴。這次第，怎一個愁字了<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">得~~~~~！ </span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌屌有無讀過書？聲聲慢啊 聲慢慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30296a958e4c554b7300118c9ec7ff7e68b202b","tid":796370,"uid":4168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"以為死咗"},{"pid":"37d6faf1eb7c6457f9b7f53ec237f221326c5c44","tid":796370,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"點解佢仲生勾勾"},{"pid":"ec38151fdd49cfbc4d4764bcb1437cbf73746fcf","tid":796370,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"過晒退休年齡仲未肯退落黎 敬業態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8619c4181c31a53f80f3c4bac39a4c8a5806472c","tid":796370,"uid":192485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3b437adffcc47f970fa10a423152643d76bb0cb5","tid":796370,"uid":152108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2be792b00e53c4a8872f17db0f660cc4b656213f","tid":796370,"uid":24160,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"e092fe401eaab6b3d0bfacc2beda4e6d3b9c731d","tid":796370,"uid":6044,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:17:19.000Z","msg":"真心講句<br />\n呢個年紀<br />\n行得走得仲唱得<br />\n佩服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後生都靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/F3QjNpm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FF3QjNpm.gif&h=d7a565b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"人瑞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/spacechannel5/images/4/47/Tumblr_m2cmxs7ncU1r6c2k5o1_500.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20120412163831\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fspacechannel5%2Fimages%2F4%2F47%2FTumblr_m2cmxs7ncU1r6c2k5o1_500.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120412163831&h=0b2e181e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個造型令我諗起呢隻驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710247449e7971203f48111d750f78470bcbfe11","tid":796370,"uid":4610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"好掛住你呀 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca22947252c696c39b3b0fd1872e38f00a594830","tid":796370,"uid":76632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770a32b49381a420355c98350753f1c1af75a05e","tid":796370,"uid":24160,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ec38151fdd49cfbc4d4764bcb1437cbf73746fcf","tid":796370,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"過晒退休年齡仲未肯退落黎 敬業態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/776df7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F776df7.jpg&h=3ccbb8ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">No!!!剛好相反!!!「退休？冇諗過。除非冇人再想睇我。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n明年將踏入半世紀演藝生涯的汪明荃（阿蛆），認為七十歲就已是「古來稀」。堅毅不屈的阿蛆表示沒有想過退休，因為牠直言不懼怕年老，儘管擔心麻煩別既照顧，但只要身體沒什麼毛病就可以繼續行下去。過往見證著一個又一個老友離㸱而去，牠更明白一個道理：想做什麼便去做，一日未死，也要繼續去做。<br />\n<br />\n見到阿蛆對「年老」有一套堅毅、樂觀同積極既睇法，就不得不回顧牠約二十歲入行時的心境。「當時18歲係有一道everlasting 既火，而家唔可以再留戀，唯一可以做既，就係要不斷push up自己！」<br />\n難怪環顧整個娛樂點圈，有阿蛆咁豐富既資歷真係十分稀有。再者，阿蛆既自強不息、堅毅積極既精神，使牠喺不論歌藝生涯，定係外在方面都一樣不斷進步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/ccab77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fccab77.jpg&h=f33769ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/a08c6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fa08c6e.jpg&h=34c73c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/13cdc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F13cdc7.jpg&h=dc566827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/79632c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F79632c.jpg&h=70e01bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/43596e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F43596e.jpg&h=325e3129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect;不屈不撓的阿蛆於㕑房地磚下仍然高聲歌唱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/vsgkml5zRqI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fvsgkml5zRqI&d=ipgdt2tu1YhOaEKRl7sZsACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=79d55c0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/vsgkml5zRqI</a><br />\nKTV版<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/LqOVt820k78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLqOVt820k78&d=ipgdt2tu1YhOaEKRl7sZsACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=44c61900\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/LqOVt820k78</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/9e80ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F9e80ad.jpg&h=4b2ce457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 力求進步阿蛆亦不斷擴濶自己既高音域，以特殊共鳴部位發聲的技巧、巧奪天工的天籟唱腔，不但穩固咗阿蛆近半世紀於樂壇殿堂級之江山地位，更將自己的唱藝事業邁向另一高峰！"}]}